  "title": "Driver",
  "description": "<ul><li>Delivery and collection of our products to designated locations, ensuring timely delivery and collection and require to do disposal of electrical appliances as needed</li><li>Conduct pre and post trip inspections, perform basic maintenance tasks</li><li>Plan and optimise routes, considering traffic, road  conditions and delivery schedules</li><li>Liaise with customers regarding delivery schedules and able to handle customers well</li><li>Loading and unloading of goods, ensuring proper securing and handling</li><li>Keep the lorry clean and tidy, both inside and outside</li><li>Help with stock management, inventory checks or warehouse tasks as needed</li><li>Able to handle physical demands, such as lifting, bending and sitting for extended period</li></ul><p>Basic Salary + Attractive Commissions Package</p>",
